Package com.github.anno4j.model.impl.selector

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataPositionSelector
    Conforms to http://www.w3.org/ns/oa#DataPositionSelector A Selector which describes a range of data based on its start and end positions within the byte stream of the representation.
    FragmentSelector
    Conforms to http://www.w3.org/ns/oa#FragmentSelector A Selector which describes the segment of interest in a representation, through the use of the fragment identifier component of a URI.
    SvgSelector
    Conforms to http://www.w3.org/TR/annotation-model/#svg-selector [subClass of oa:Selector] The class for a Selector which defines a shape using the SVG standard.
    TextPositionSelector
    Conforms to http://www.w3.org/ns/oa#TextPositionSelector An oa:Selector which describes a range of text based on its start and end positions.
    TextQuoteSelector
    Conforms to http://www.w3.org/ns/oa#TextQuoteSelector A Selector that describes a textual segment by means of quoting it, plus passages before or after it.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FragmentSpecification
    Enum contains the specifications that a FragmentSelector can be conform to.
